timelineItems.name: Don
timelineItems.text: I got $10 on Arnaud eating Ozzie Alonso before the night is out. #dcuafterdark #dcu

timelineItems.name: DC United WUFC
timelineItems.text: I can only deal w/ one glass man at a time. Pontius currently, & forever, is the injury-prone one I fret over. Get better pls Silva. #DCU -L
